headline: Lennox (NYSE:LII): Strongest Q3 Results from the HVAC and Water Systems Group
summary: The end of the earnings season is always a good time to take a step back and see who shined (and who not so much). Let’s take a look at how hvac and water systems stocks fared in Q3, starting with Lennox (NYSE:LII).
